This is a Chrome extension adds a a menu item to the context menu so that when you have text selected and you right click you can render the selected text as HTML in a new tab. Use it when viewing example html snippets on sites like stackoverflow, github, or other sites

Chrome Webstore Link
https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/jcmgcgddggonhfmkjkogkmifcfmkmgfg/publish-accepted

